**Demonized** | Attribute
__Basics__
The attribute of the underworld team. Demonized players will turn into an undead if they die during the night.

__Formalized__
Starting: Protect @Self from `Kills` through `Recruitment Defense` during Night (~UntilUse)
On Recruitment Defense: Role Change @Self to `Undead`
On Role Change: (@Self->Alignment is not `Underworld`) and not (@Self has `Defense:Recruitment:@Self`): Protect @Self from `Attacks` through `Recruitment Defense` during Night (~Persistent)
